dc_description_s: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase NVilas_PLSS_2017.gdbN. [The current control point on the surface of the earth and its associated current coordinate value, generally determined by a surveying process and used to define an extremity of a boundary.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: Vilas County Land Information and Mapping Department
